Therefore, cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also analyzes the learning dynamics using dynamical system theory, which falls under the category of control theory and systems engineering, indicating cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses various games and their equilibria, which is a topic of interest in game theory, suggesting cs.GT (Game Theory) as another possible sub-category.
